simulation_12C: simulation for 12C(p,p')3alpha
simulation_34Ar: simulation for 34Ar(alpha,p)37K
simulation_geometrical_efficiency: calculate geomtrical efficiency of atomx si arrays as a functions of reaction-z (no gas is used for this example)

common/atomx_simulation_script_writter.py: python class atomx_simulation_script_writter for creating configuration files and run scripts
